import { 
  Box,
  Button,
  Typography,
  Slider
} from '@material-ui/core';

import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'
import { faDrum, faMicrophoneLines, faGuitar, faMusic } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'

import '../styling/remix.css';

import RemixComponent from './remixComponent';

import Ctrl from '../ctrl.jpg';

const Remix = () => {  
  return(
    <Box
      id='remix-window'
    >
      <Typography id='remixes'>Stem Remix</Typography>
      <Box
        display='flex'
        flexDirection='column'
      >
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faMicrophoneLines} />
        Vocals
      </Box>

      <Box
        display='flex'
        flexDirection='column'
      >
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faDrum} />
        Drums
        <Slider disabled defaultValue={30} aria-label="Disabled slider" />
      </Box>
      <Box
        display='flex'
        flexDirection='column'
      >
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faGuitar} />
        Bass
      </Box>
      <Box
        display='flex'
        flexDirection='column'
      >
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faMusic} />
        Other
      </Box>
    </Box>
    )
}

export default Remix;
